---
description: List every registered cron job with its schedule (static AST scan of app/jobs/).
allowed-tools: Bash(gofasta inspect-jobs*)
argument-hint: [<job-name>]
---

Run `gofasta inspect-jobs $ARGUMENTS --json`. Report each job's name,
type, schedule (from config.yaml), and source file. Use this before
adding a new job to avoid name collisions or schedule overlaps.
